    {
      "current": "QQ联系人:岛岛(2926855205)发来了消息:[图片]\n^system:20260326_084741:这张图片的内容是：这是一个Python官方网站的页面，展示了Python 3.12.10版本的发布信息。\n\n页面顶部是蓝色的导航栏，包含Python标志、\"Donate\"按钮、搜索框和\"GO\"按钮，以及\"Socialize\"链接。导航菜单项有\"About\", \"Downloads\", \"Documentation\", \"Community\", \"Success Stories\", \"News\", \"Events\"。\n\n页面主体内容：\n标题：Python 3.12.10\n提示：Note: Python 3.12.10 has been superseded by Python 3.12.13.\n发布日期：Release date: April 8, 2025\n主标题：This is the tenth maintenance release of Python 3.12\n描述：Python 3.12.10 is the latest maintenance release of Python 3.12, and the last full maintenance release. Subsequent releases of 3.12 will be security-fixes only. This last maintenance release contains about 230 bugfixes, build improvements and documentation changes since 3.12.9.\n\n副标题：Major new features of the 3.12 series, compared to 3.11\n子标题：New features\n列表项：\n* More flexible f-string parsing, allowing many things previously disallowed (PEP 701).\n* Support for the buffer protocol in Python code (PEP 688).\n* A new debugging/profiling API (PEP 669).\n* Support for isolated subinterpreters with separate Global Interpreter Locks (PEP 684).\n* Even more improved error messages. More exceptions potentially caused by typos now make suggestions to the user.\n* Support for the Linux perf",
